Package: traitheritage
Type: Package
Title: Inferential Methods for Phylogenetic Trait Heritage
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sam", "Passmore", email = "u1123115@anu.edu.au",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides inferential methods for calculating the phylogenetic
    heritage of taxa traits. Functions estimate the probability that pairs of
    taxa share a trait as a function of their shared evolutionary history,
    support co-evolution analyses combining trait similarity and geographic
    distance, and can be applied across posterior samples of phylogenetic trees.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/SamPassmore/traitheritage
BugReports: https://github.com/SamPassmore/traitheritage/issues
